sakaki-i3-dotfiles
==================
Repository containing my X11/i3wm configuration files.

* currently present:
--------------------
"$HOME"/.bashrc # "shell config/autostart"
"$HOME"/.bash_profile # "profile autostart"
"$HOME"/.config/i3 # wm
"$HOME"/.config/i3blocks # i3 custom bar
"$HOME"/.config/kitty # terminal
"$HOME"/.config/rofi # dmenu alternative
"$HOME"/.local/bin/protonmananager # protonGE manager
"$HOME"/.local/bin/slackmount # slack disk mounter
"$HOME"/.local/bin/basicc # basic calculator

installation:
-------------
$ sudo pacman -S feh kitty rofi i3 ttf-iosevka-nerd
$ (git clone https://github.com/sakaki91/sakaki-i3-dotfiles && cd sakaki-i3-dotfiles && ./install.sh)
